	   <tr><td colspan=2>Sad..sad...sad, all you newbie wizzys are posting about an effective way to solo, and what? going on now about agility stats?<br><br>lol, come on give it up, verant is @#%^ing stupid,<br>"masters of defense" bah, thats a statment that has been totally disregarded by wizards since release. The strategies that are implemented in the game now,were &gt;PLAYER MADE&lt; meaning everything you see now, from how lguk is camped. how sebilis is camped was set up by players, EVERYTHING&lt; and thats because for whatever reason, how the classes were supposed to work out, they didnt according to what they were given and it just stayed like that.<br><br>I hate to break your spirits but its not poosible to turn wizards or any pure caster into a sufficiant tank. IF it was even possible, things at higher levels melee in regular dungeons, for double 140, wizards hitpoints to not exceed 1500 and thats way pushing it with 52+ cleric buffs, i have 140 agility and mainly because it helps out when i get aggroed which i dont often,(being a good wiz) and i will still get raped by greens or blues, if it doesnt get off me in under id say about 20 seconds.<br><br>Wizards are not and never will be made to tank, it may be hard to believe but as you get higher, you will be less and less getting hit or you will not be going up in levels anymore, you will be dieing,<br><br>And I also have something quick to say about wizards solo'ing from 29 to 52 like that xev person or whatever, PLEASE QUIT YOUR WIZ&lt; if i was any class i would not group with you as you prolly have no @#%^ing clue on how to group anymore,i would NEVER EVER recommend soloing as a wiz if you plan to get 60, get uber, get good items whatever, <br><br>Their is no way, no way, you will be able to survive if you dont learn how to be a wiz and that doenst happen by cheap ass kiting threw those levels, it may be easy, but its boring as hell and it makes the game a chore, and last time i checked this was a @#%^ing video game.<br><br>SO all you wizards out their that plan on solo'ing to 60_ its not going to happen, dont count on being liked, dont count on getting groups anywhere, and i wouldnt count on having fun with the game either because kiting for 20 levels is probly the most boring thing ive ever heard,<br><br><br><br>BE GOOD WIZARD&lt; KNOW YOUR ROLE<br>58 EVOKER______BRISTLEBANE<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
